COURTNEY
He couldn't handle me.
VINCE (30's, wannabe Alpha) does a double-take. Hooked.
FAITH
Right, just so I'm clear: you were
the one who filed for divorce then?
Courtney looks away. Humiliated. Her cheeks flush with
embarrassment. That's a "no."
Faith makes a mark in her notes as Justin turns to Courtney.
JUSTIN
You okay?
Faith hears this and turns on a heel. Looks right at him.
