116 INT. FAITH'S FANCY NEW D.A. OFFICE - DAY 116
Boxes and file crates everywhere. Faith at her desk, staring
into nothing. Thinking.
She's so lost in thought she doesn't notice RESNICK enter.
He hands her a PLANT.
RESNICK
For the new digs.
FAITH
Thanks.
She sets it down as he looks around the office.
RESNICK
